---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Hobby" current="/hobby">

<div class="page-header">
  <div class="eyebrow">// outside the lab</div>
  <h1>Hobby</h1>
  <p>Things I do when I'm not writing code or reading papers.</p>
</div>

<div class="hobby-grid">
  <div class="hobby-card">
    <span class="icon">🔭</span>
    <h3>Astronomy</h3>
    <p>Astrophotography and observational astronomy. Particularly interested in deep-sky objects and long-exposure imaging.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="hobby-card">
    <span class="icon">🧬</span>
    <h3>Biology & Genetics</h3>
    <p>Reading about molecular biology, evolution and the science behind the data I work with. Genomics makes more sense when you find it genuinely interesting.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="hobby-card">
    <span class="icon">🔌</span>
    <h3>Electronics</h3>
    <p>Breadboards, microcontrollers, sensors. Building things that interact with the physical world — same impulse behind the ECG hardware project.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="hobby-card">
    <span class="icon">🏔️</span>
    <h3>Hiking</h3>
    <p>Mountains and trails — Tatry, Beskidy. Long walks with no screens are good for thinking through hard problems.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="hobby-card">
    <span class="icon">📐</span>
    <h3>Mathematics</h3>
    <p>Recreational math, number theory, puzzles. Math for its own sake — not just as a tool for ML.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="hobby-card">
    <span class="icon">🌐</span>
    <h3>Homelab & Networks</h3>
    <p>Running local servers, experimenting with VLANs and network configurations. The home version of what I do professionally.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="hobby-card">
    <span class="icon">🎮</span>
    <h3>Game Development</h3>
    <p>Building games in Godot — more interested in the software architecture and systems design than the game itself.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="hobby-card">
    <span class="icon">♟️</span>
    <h3>Strategy Games</h3>
    <p>Grand strategy, city builders, simulation. Appreciate games with deep underlying systems and emergent behavior.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="hobby-card">
    <span class="icon">📚</span>
    <h3>Reading</h3>
    <p>AI research papers, popular science, medicine. Trying to stay informed about the frontier of ML and biology.</p>
  </div>
</div>

</Layout>
